77
00:08:23,850 --> 00:08:26,119
<font color=#FFFF00>Ini sudah larut malam. Pulanglah.</font>

78
00:08:29,590 --> 00:08:30,590
<font color=#FFFF00>Sampai nanti.</font>

79
00:10:19,460 --> 00:10:20,470
<font color=#FFFF00>Bagaimana keadaan Pil Joo?</font>

80
