123
00:15:52,399 --> 00:15:54,970
<font color=#FFFF00>Itu mungkin benar. Tapi...</font>

124
00:16:03,940 --> 00:16:05,810
<font color=#FFFF00>Eksekutif Jung, selamat datang.</font>

125
00:16:06,040 --> 00:16:08,479
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku seharusnya mengunjungi Anda di Mooshimwon lebih dahulu,</font>

126
00:16:08,509 --> 00:16:11,320
