146
00:17:29,429 --> 00:17:30,760
<font color=#FFFF00>karena aku tidak mau melihatnya terbaring sakit.</font>

147
00:17:33,169 --> 00:17:34,500
<font color=#FFFF00>Tapi aku berubah pikiran.</font>

148
00:17:35,330 --> 00:17:36,699
